structured_scope.description:
The content of the structured_scope claim of the the new token in URL encoded - Base64 encoded JSON.
To be handled as PATCH (only claims/subclaims mentioned are updated, others stay as they are in the previous token).
Example content: {"sign":{"documentDigests":[{"hash":"sTOgwOm+474gFj0q0x1iSNspKqbcse4IeiqlDg/HWuI2"}]}}
